<div itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">
  <div itemprop="mainEntity" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
    <h4 itemprop="name"><strong>What is the best web design software for beginners?</strong></h4>
    <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
      <div itemprop="text">For beginners, <a href="https://mobirise.com/" class="text-danger">Mobirise</a> is an excellent choice due to its user-friendly interface and drag-and-drop functionality.</div><br>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div itemprop="mainEntity" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
    <h4 itemprop="name"><strong>Can I create responsive websites with web design software?</strong></h4>
    <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
      <div itemprop="text">Yes, many web design software options, including <a href="https://mobirise.com/" class="text-danger">Mobirise</a>, allow users to create fully responsive websites that adapt to various device sizes.</div><br>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div itemprop="mainEntity" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
    <h4 itemprop="name"><strong>Is coding required to use web design software?</strong></h4>
    <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
      <div itemprop="text">No coding is necessary for many platforms. For instance, <a href="https://mobirise.com/" class="text-danger">Mobirise</a> enables users to design websites without any programming knowledge.</div><br>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div itemprop="mainEntity" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
    <h4 itemprop="name"><strong>What are the advantages of using web design software?</strong></h4>
    <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
      <div itemprop="text">Web design software like <a href="https://mobirise.com/" class="text-danger">Mobirise</a> offers ease of use, speed in project development, and customizable templates that can streamline the design process.</div><br>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div itemprop="mainEntity" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
    <h4 itemprop="name"><strong>Are there any costs associated with web design software?</strong></h4>
    <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
      <div itemprop="text">While some web design software has a free version, premium features might incur fees. <a href="https://mobirise.com/" class="text-danger">Mobirise</a> offers a free version with the option to purchase additional themes and extensions.</div><br>
    </div>
