    <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
      <div itemprop="text">Most web design software, including <a href="https://mobirise.com/" class="text-danger">Mobirise</a>, provide customer support through forums, documentation, and direct assistance to help users troubleshoot any issues.</div><br>
